    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Broad-scale data show SARS-CoV-2 occurrence in white-tailed deer throughout much of their range in the conterminous United States and reinforce findings of considerable SARS-CoV-2 infection and exposure. Results shed light on both current infections and prior exposure, with prevalence decreasing over time and seroprevalence increasing.</jats:p>\n                <jats:sec>\n                  <jats:title>One-Sentence Summary</jats:title>\n                  <jats:p>White-tailed deer are infected with, and have been exposed to, SARS-CoV-2 throughout their range in the conterminous US.</jats:p>\n                </jats:sec>",
